Summary: This event was captured on my cell phone. I was taking a picture of the beam of light coming through the clouds not the object in the pic.
divs: sighting detailsi was on my way to nashville, tn from my home in bruceton, tn. it was an overcast day as you can see in the picture. i was traveling south on hwy 641 in benton co when this beam of light came through the clouds of course i thought at the time it was the sun breaking through. i thought this would be a cool picture so i took out my cell phone and shot the picture never thinking nothing of it other than it being a nice picture. this happened approx. 4-5 yrs ago. today on 1\12\11 for no good reason while watching a program on tv that had absolutely nothing to do with ufos i thought about this picture and how i would like to have it as a background picture for my desktop. so i sent it to my email and downloaded it. when i first saw it enlarged on my computer i thought it was a speck of dirt on the screen then after close inspection of it i now think i may have inadvertently caught a ufo in the picture. i may be wrong but i don't think so. take a look and with better software than i have maybe you can figure out what it is.
